<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="1" >
<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal" style="font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><span style="line-height: 17.12px; background: white;">Hi {!Lead.FirstName},<br></span><span style="line-height: 17.12px;"><br>I’ve not been able to reach you today regarding your request for an insurance quote via our partner, Swoop.<br></span></font><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>It will only take 5-10 minutes to provide you with a comprehensive quote.&nbsp;</span><b style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><a href="https://calendly.com/d/cm2p-trc-cnn/kingsbridge-insurance-call-back-swoop">Book a call with me today.</a></b><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><b>&nbsp;<br></b></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><b><br></b>Here at Kingsbridge we offer several complete packages of cover that are designed specifically for UK businesses.<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br><b>Why buy with Kingsbridge?</b></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="font-size: 12pt;"></p><ul style="font-size: 12pt;"><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><b>Tailored solutions:&nbsp;</b>Coverage is specifically designed for contractors, freelancers, and small businesses, so you get protection that meets your needs.</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><b>Dedicated support:&nbsp;</b>Kingsbridge’s in-house claims and underwriting teams work closely with you and the insurer, providing guidance and peace of mind throughout your policy.&nbsp;</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><b>Proven customer satisfaction:</b>&nbsp;With customer ratings of 4.8/5 on Feefo and 4.6/5 on Google, Kingsbridge has a reputation for excellent service.</font></li></ul><p style="font-size: 12pt;"></p><div><font style="font-size: 12pt;">So that I can discuss which of our schemes would be most relevant for your business, it would be good to speak over the phone.&nbsp;</font><b style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><a href="https://calendly.com/d/cm2p-trc-cnn/kingsbridge-insurance-call-back-swoop">Book a call with me</a>.<br></b><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>Alternatively, you can reply to&nbsp;</span><font face="Arial, sans-serif">let me know a good time to call or&nbsp;</font><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">contact me on</span><b style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;01242 808 740</b><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">. Our office is open between the hours of 8:00am-5:30pm, Monday-Friday.&nbsp;</span></div><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>I look forward to hearing from you.&nbsp;<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="background-color: white;"><br>Kind regards,<br></span></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>{!User.FirstName}&nbsp;<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Sales Team<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>E: salesteam@kingsbridge.co.uk<br></span><font style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">T:&nbsp;</font><font style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">01242 808740</font></div>]]></td>
</tr>
